cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper deals with implementing artificial neural networks on neuromorphic architectures, which falls under the category of computational neuroscience (cs.NE) and electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET). The paper also involves optimization techniques (cs.AR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the form of deep neural networks. Finally, the paper deals with the implementation of neural networks on hardware (cs.SY), specifically neuromorphic chips.
